    "320": "Small cards, mobile UI, dense lists",
    "640": "Default card/sidebar usage",
    "960": "Large desktop cards or hero-like panels only"
  },
  "usageRules": [
    "Use as decorative images with alt=\"\" and aria-hidden=\"true\" unless the scene itself is the content.",
    "Prefer 320 for mobile cards, 640 for normal desktop cards, 960 only for large panels.",
    "Reserve image dimensions or aspect ratio to prevent layout shift.",
    "Lazy-load below-the-fold scenes; use priority only for an above-the-fold hero.",
    "Do not place readable text on top of detailed image areas.",
    "Do not commit source PNG regeneration files; keep only optimized runtime WebP variants."
